These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, apple, pear, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, japanese, indonesian
1. the argentine is on the left of the australian##1
2. the person eating apricot is the indonesian##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person eating apple is on the left of the indonesian##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | artichoke | pear | apple | apricot   |
| Nationality   | argentine  | australian     | japanese   | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, magic-tricks, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | drawing | writing    |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | baseball      | cycling | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, skydiving, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, documentary, comedy
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | collecting | drawing | skydiving   | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | documentary | comedy | sports         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, family, thriller, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, rowing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | family | romance  | thriller      |
| Sport         | golf | skiing   | rowing | cycling |

