.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, kale, radish
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, snake, chinchilla
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating kale##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | radish | kale | watermelon | asparagus |
| Pet    | guinea-pig       | chinchilla | snake | lizard     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
