3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | british | australian |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | horse | cat | pony    |

