.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, hip-hop, punk
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
2. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | d&b | country | punk  |
| Pet           | dog | lizard | fish       | goat |

