.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, photographer, dressmaker, firefighter
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, subway, boat, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the photographer##1
2. the person driving the ship is the firefighter##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | dressmaker | bartender      | photographer | firefighter |
| Transport   | airplane          | subway | boat     | ship    |

