.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, quad-bike, car
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade | coffee  | soy-milk | almond-milk |
| Transport   | car | quad-bike | subway          | roller    |

