.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, classical, soul
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee  | fanta | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | country  | classical | soul           | funk   |

