3. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | lemonade  | cola | 7up   |
| Pet        | turtle | dog | bird    | mouse |

