.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, german, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, trike, subway
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the italian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the german##1
4. the italian is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | german | indonesian | italian   |
| Transport     | trike  | tram    | motorbike       | subway |

 